<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- mạbtḥlạsẖ gẖyr lmạ nʿysẖhạ fy rḍạk wfy ḥbk wfy ḍlk
 wmạyhwnhạsẖ gẖyrk fyhạ wạ̹nt sẖạylnạ kạ̉b fy ḥḍnk
 1- wmạsẖfnạsẖ fyhạ ḍyq ạmtdt ạ̹lạ wkạn lyhạ ḥd wqạdt
 fy ḍyạʾ nqwl ạḥdẖr tqwl frjt lmạ tqwl llḍyq ạtạkẖr
 wbtfrḥ bslạmẗ bʿbdk wbtfrḥ bslạmẗ bʿbdk
 2- wmạsẖfnạsẖ fyhạ ḥd ykẖṣk wạtkẖlyt ʿnh fy ạ̉zmạth
 wlạ ạ̉wlạdh ạḥtạjh lgẖyrk bl ạ̉gẖnyt gẖyrh bkẖyrạth
 wạlnạs sẖhdt fyh lạ̉mạntk ạlnạs sẖhdt fyh lạ̉mạntk
 3- wmạsẖfnạsẖ ạlʿtmẗ btqʿd fwq wqthạ ʿlsẖạn mtḥdd
 ḥty̱ ạlẓlm ạ̹n kạn mtsyd yhrb qdạm wjh ạlsyd
 lmạ tqwl ytbdd kẖṣmk lmạ tqwl ytbdd kẖṣmk
 4- wmạsẖfnạsẖ sẖryr ạtbạhy̱ wʿlạ fy ṣwth wạ̹ydh ʿlạhạ
 ạ̹lạ wrạḥ bsẖrwrh ạ̹yạhạ wạtrd fy lylẗ wḍḥạhạ
 sẖrh ʿlyh wkẖyrk ʿly̱ sẖʿbk sẖrh ʿlyh wkẖyrk ʿly̱ sẖʿbk
 5- wmạsẖfnạsẖ fyhạ ạstqrạr wlạ rạḥẗ wlạ ḥty̱ dyạr
 ạsẖtqnạlk wạlmsẖwạr ṭwl wạlạ̉yạm btṭwl
 ạsndnạ wṣbrnạ bqrbk ạsndnạ wṣbrnạ bqrbk</lyrics>
<title>mạ btḥlạsẖ</title>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
